First, let's start what money is. Sounds simple, but I bet you that only top 1% really understand what money is. I am certainly not in that 1%. In my research I found MIT course  
'Blockchain and Money', by Prof. Gary Gensler very informative. Its more than 30+ hour, but definitely worht your time. 

